root: ^!Without any of the creepy ambiance like last time, Jade let me into her home.
^%Wait here for a moment. I’ll be right back.
^!Jade walks off down a corridor, her boot heels echoing through the halls of her estate.
^!Distant howls echo from some place I can’t see and there’s a faint scratching sound, like claws on tile.
^!I cautiously peek down the hall and find stall after stall of scared looking dogs. A few of them notice me and skitter up to the chain link fence, sticking their noses through to sniff at the air.
